    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile,<strong> </strong>remove the string from your <strong>lamb leg joint[s]</strong>, then pat dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Rub the <strong>lamb leg joint[s] </strong>with a drizzle of<strong> olive oil</strong> and season with your <strong>Mediterranean-style seasoning</strong> and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p>",
