    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>tomato & pepper garlic potatoes </strong>with the<strong> sliced kleftiko-style lamb </strong>to the side</p><p>Squeeze the <strong>roasted lemon juice </strong>over the top (not sure about citrus? Try using less!)</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>chopped parsley</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
